, l</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">ittle has been done by Government to address these issues</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. S</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">uch work as has been undertaken </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">by the Government </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">and others </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">has further cast doubt on the strategic case.</span></li><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 32pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">T</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">he arguments </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">put forward </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">by the DfT </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">for continuing with HS2 have shifted</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">since 2011</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. M</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">ore emphasis </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">is </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">now </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">placed on:</span></li></ol><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 62.68pt; padding-left:9.32pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">it’s not about speed it is about providing capacity</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </spa