ew Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal">32% full</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> and about </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal">50% full</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">in</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> peak hours. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">It is the second emptiest of the main line service</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">s. The emptiest is H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">S1</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> from </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">London</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> to Folkestone.</span></li><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">T</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">he </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">WCML</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">and </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">its Euston terminus</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">are</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">clearly </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">not</span><span s